with their eyes set on the stars.</i>

00:32.083 --> 00:35.083
BASED ON REAL EVENTS

00:45.583 --> 00:48.541
<i>She was destined to be someone important.</i>

00:50.750 --> 00:53.125
<i>She was supposed
to be the first among all of us.</i>

00:56.458 --> 01:00.791
<i>She came into this world to change it,
but she didn't have the time.</i>

01:03.500 --> 01:05.458
<i>There were three shots.</i>

01:05.458 --> 01:08.833
<i>One to the face, one to the chest,</i>

01:09.708 --> 01:11.541
