01:52.125 --> 01:56.000
<i>My name is Aurora Rodríguez Carballeira.
I am Hildegart's mother.</i>

01:57.166 --> 01:59.666
<i>Thanks to my intellectual avidity
and my father's fortune,</i>

01:59.666 --> 02:01.041
