10:53.625 --> 10:54.708
Hildegart!

10:54.708 --> 10:59.083
Workers to power! Workers to power!

11:00.583 --> 11:01.708
Look at the camera!

11:04.083 --> 11:06.458
Spain is not Catholic anymore!

11:06.458 --> 11:09.583
