01:23:50.041 --> 01:23:51.500
"sigh no more.

01:23:52.625 --> 01:23:54.541
"Men were deceivers ever.

01:23:55.750 --> 01:23:57.333
"One foot in sea,

01:23:58.000 --> 01:23:59.625
"and one on shore,

01:24:00.125 --> 01:24:02.208
