01:25:33.375 --> 01:25:34.958
What happened to Macarena?

01:25:36.083 --> 01:25:37.958
Did she quit or did you fire her?

01:25:41.791 --> 01:25:43.208
That's not important.

01:25:45.166 --> 01:25:47.125
