01:25:55.291 --> 01:25:56.541
I'll get it.

01:25:56.541 --> 01:25:58.083
Maybe it's Macarena.

01:26:01.750 --> 01:26:03.083
Hildegart.

01:26:05.250 --> 01:26:07.083
Abel came to see me
before he was arrested.

01:26:07.083 --> 01:26:08.208
No, no. Please.

01:26:08.208 --> 01:26:10.791
- He asked me to...
