01:27:49.541 --> 01:27:50.666
This is our house.

01:27:50.666 --> 01:27:52.958
I'm sorry. This is the last thing
I wanted to happen.

01:27:52.958 --> 01:27:54.625
I hope you can forgive me.

01:27:54.625 --> 01:27:55.875
Here's the living room.

01:27:55.875 --> 01:27:58.000
Come this way, please.

01:27:58.666 --> 01:27:59.833
Here's the...

01:28:01.166 --> 01:28:04.208
- What are you doing here?
- I needed to eat before I kept going.

01:28:04.833 --> 01:28:06.791
I'm sorry, this is my daughter, Hildegart.

01:28:07.500 --> 01:28:09.375
- Nice to meet you.
- Pleased to meet you.

01:28:09.375 --> 01:28:11.916
People talk a lot about your books.

01:28:11.916 --> 01:28:13.416
Have you read any?

01:28:13.416 --> 01:28:15.708
No, I can't read.

01:28:16.583 --> 01:28:17.958
Shall we continue?

01:28:17.958 --> 01:28:19.291
This way.

