was the creation of that human being.

01:43:56.875 --> 01:43:59.708
Invigorating,
drop by drop, my belief in her.

01:44:05.500 --> 01:44:06.791
But you men,

01:44:08.125 --> 01:44:09.458
distracted,

01:44:10.458 --> 01:44:13.291
